arStrings.szText: When you Stun, {c_important}{u}Freeze{/u}{/c}, or Immobilize an Elite enemy, or damage a Boss, it Pulls In Nearby enemies. You deal {c_random}[Affix_Value_1|%x|]{/c} increased damage to them for {c_number}[Affix."Static Value 0"]{/c} seconds. This effect can only occur once every {c_number}[Affix."Static Value 1"]{/c} seconds.
